-- Telecom Italia May Be Asked to Drop Its Argentina Stake Option, MF Reports
-- Armorel Kenna
-- 2010-07-13T06:42:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/telecom-italia-may-be-asked-to-drop-its-argentina-stake-option-mf-reports.html

          
          
             Telecom Italia SpA may be asked to
renounce its option to raise its stake in the company that
controls Telecom Argentina SA, newspaper MF reported, without
saying where it got the information.  
 The Argentine government may allow Telecom Italia to keep
its 50 percent stake in the company that controls Telecom
Argentina and in exchange allow local investors to buy the
remainder, according to the Italian newspaper.  
          
          


  


        